\n\n[ux_image id=\"53\" width=\"20\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"1.45\" line_height=\"1\"]\n\n<h3>Services that connect you to your users</h3>\n\n[/ux_text]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[row style=\"small\" col_bg=\"rgb(253, 252, 255)\" col_bg_radius=\"5\" v_align=\"equal\" padding=\"70px 40px 70px 40px\" padding__md=\"30px 20px 30px 20px\" depth_hover=\"3\"]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\" bg_color=\"rgb(255, 250, 238)\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"44\" img_width=\"50\" pos=\"center\" link=\"#\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"0.85\" font_size__md=\"1\"]\n\n<h2>Design</h2>\n\n[/ux_text]\n[gap height=\"10px\"]\n\n<p>A dedicated team of UX/UI designers unveiling the full potential of being design-driven.</p>\n\n[button text=\"Learn more\" color=\"secondary\" style=\"link\" size=\"small\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\" bg_color=\"rgb(235, 241, 251)\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"45\" img_width=\"50\" pos=\"center\" link=\"#\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"0.85\" font_size__md=\"1\"]\n\n<h2>Application Development</h2>\n\n[/ux_text]\n[gap height=\"10px\"]\n\n<p>We build stunning apps that capture the users\' imaginations.</p>\n\n[button text=\"Learn more\" color=\"secondary\" style=\"link\" size=\"small\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\" bg_color=\"rgb(255, 241, 250)\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"49\" img_width=\"50\" pos=\"center\" link=\"#\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"0.85\" font_size__md=\"1\"]\n\n<h2>Cloud</h2>\n\n[/ux_text]\n[gap height=\"10px\"]\n\n<p>Cloud hosting services that perfectly fit small and large businesses.</p>\n\n[button text=\"Learn more\" color=\"secondary\" style=\"link\" size=\"small\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\" bg_color=\"rgb(237, 250, 254)\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"47\" img_width=\"50\" pos=\"center\" link=\"#\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"0.85\" font_size__md=\"1\"]\n\n<h2>IT Services</h2>\n\n[/ux_text]\n[gap height=\"10px\"]\n\n<p>Our full range of IT services is a one-stop solution for your business.</p>\n\n[button text=\"Learn more\" color=\"secondary\" style=\"link\" size=\"small\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\" bg_color=\"rgb(241, 234, 254)\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"46\" img_width=\"50\" pos=\"center\" link=\"#\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"0.85\" font_size__md=\"1\"]\n\n<h2>System and Software</h2>\n\n[/ux_text]\n[gap height=\"10px\"]\n\n<p>Creating scalable engineering solutions with an agile architectural backbone.</p>\n\n[button text=\"Learn more\" color=\"secondary\" style=\"link\" size=\"small\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\" bg_color=\"rgb(228, 248, 246)\"]\n\n[featured_box img=\"48\" img_width=\"50\" pos=\"center\" link=\"#\"]\n\n[ux_text font_size=\"0.85\" font_size__md=\"1\"]\n\n<h2>Software Testing</h2>\n\n[/ux_text]\n[gap height=\"10px\"]\n\n<p>Confidently deliver software faster with our <strong>robust QA processes</strong>.</p>\n[button text=\"Learn more\" color=\"secondary\" style=\"link\" size=\"small\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->', 'suyogtech', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-03-14 19:16:12', '2022-03-14 19:16:12', '', 13, 'http://iespl.in/suyogtech/?p=55', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
